<Layout title="About">
  <h1>About Savage Bushido</h1>
  <p>Savage Bushido adapts the classic 1981 Bushido RPG by Bob Charrette and Paul Hume into the Savage Worlds Adventure Edition rules.</p>
  <p>It is set in Nippon — a mythical warring-states Japan — where honor, steel, and the spirit world shape every life.</p>
